==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: lap up
<hw>lap up</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See <er>lap</er>,
<pos>v. i.</pos>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To take up (drink or food) with
the tongue; to drink by licking up.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <mark>(fig.)</mark> <def>To accept or enjoy
enthusiatically and uncritically; <as>as, to <ex>lap up</ex>
praise</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Laputan</ent>⟦br⟧
